description.en: I'm late! I'm late! For a very important date! No time to say hello, goodbye! I'm late! This tardy little guy follows his master around picking up dropped items.
description.ar: I'm late! I'm late! For a very important date! No time to say hello, goodbye! I'm late! This tardy little guy follows his master around picking up dropped items.
description.br: Estou atrasado!  Apressado, sem tempo para dizer oi, tchau! Atrasado!  Este coelho apressado segue seu mestre e coleta itens caídos do chão.
description.cns: “快迟到了！快迟到了！我要去赶一场非常重要的约会！没时间打招呼了，再见！来不及了！”，这只慢吞吞的小家伙会跟随它的主人并捡起周围掉落的物品。
description.de: Weißes Kaninchen, das dir überall hin folgt und Gegenstände für dich aufsammelt, wenn es Zeit dazu hat.
description.fi: I'm late! I'm late! For a very important date! No time to say hello, goodbye! I'm late! This tardy little guy follows his master around picking up dropped items.
description.fil: I'm late! I'm late! For a very important date! No time to say hello, goodbye! I'm late! This tardy little guy follows his master around picking up dropped items.
description.fr: Je suis en retard ! En retard ! En retard !
description.id: Aku terlambat! Aku terlambat! Untuk hari yang sangat penting! Tidak ada waktu untuk menyapa, selamat tinggal! Aku terlambat! Si kecil yang terlambat ini mengikuti tuannya berkeliling mengambil barang-barang yang jatuh.
description.it: I'm late! I'm late! For a very important date! No time to say hello, goodbye! I'm late! This tardy little guy follows his master around picking up dropped items.
description.jp: 遅刻だ！遅刻だ！こんな大事な日に！挨拶する時間はないよ、バイバイ！あわてんぼうのこのうさぎさんは、ご主人様の落し物を拾って回ります。
description.kr: 나는 늦었다! 나는 늦었다! 아주 중요한 데이트를 위해! 인사 할 시간이 없어요, 안녕! 나는 늦었다! 이 지각 한 작은 녀석은 떨어 뜨린 물건을 집어 들고 주인을 따라갑니다.
description.nl: I'm late! I'm late! For a very important date! No time to say hello, goodbye! I'm late! This tardy little guy follows his master around picking up dropped items.
description.pl: I'm late! I'm late! For a very important date! No time to say hello, goodbye! I'm late! This tardy little guy follows his master around picking up dropped items.
description.ru: Белый кролик, явно сбежавший из Страны Чудес. Теперь он будет следовать за вами и собирать предметы.
description.sp: ¡Voy tarde! ¡Voy tarde! ¡A una cita muy importante! ¡No tengo tiempo de decir hola, adiós! ¡Voy tarde! Este pequeño tardón sigue a su dueño y recoge los objetos soltados.
description.sw: I'm late! I'm late! For a very important date! No time to say hello, goodbye! I'm late! This tardy little guy follows his master around picking up dropped items.
description.th: ฉันสาย! ฉันสาย! สำหรับวันที่สำคัญมาก! ไม่มีเวลามาทักทาย ลาก่อน! ฉันสาย! เจ้าตัวน้อยที่เดินช้าตามเจ้านายของเขาไปเก็บสิ่งของที่หล่นลงมา
description.vi: Tôi trễ! Tôi trễ! Cho một ngày rất quan trọng! Không có thời gian để nói xin chào, tạm biệt! Tôi trễ! Anh chàng chậm chạp này đi theo chủ nhân của mình để nhặt những món đồ bị đánh rơi.
